uk.ac.warwick.dcs.sherlock.api.model.detection

Class AbstractPairwiseDetector<T extends AbstractPairwiseDetectorWorker>

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.warwick.dcs.sherlock.api.model.detection.AbstractPairwiseDetector<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IDetector<T>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    NGramDetector, TestDetector

    public abstract class AbstractPairwiseDetector<T extends AbstractPairwiseDetectorWorker>
extends java.lang.Object
implements IDetector<T>
    An abstract IDetector implementation which constructs an individual, parallel worker for each combination of files in the dataset. This can be used as a base for pairwise matching algorithms.

    More advanced implementations should directly implement the IDetector interface.
